lead_paragraph: Purdue wasn't at full strength with freshman standout Caleb Swanigan on the bench. The Boilermakers weren't at full attention, either, considering how many times Minnesota dribbled by them for layups and dunks.

headline.print_headline: No. 21 Purdue Tops Minnesota 68-64 With 24 Points by Edwards
